{"type": "article", "id": 29327, "title": "这个摄影博物馆的墙面，灵感源于镜头光圈", "description": "博物馆的设计连接了传统和现代，就像是这个家族所经历的历史。", "date": "2016-07-08T23:03:16Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 29964, "name": "阿尔巴尼亚"}, {"id": 29965, "name": "摄影博物馆"}, {"id": 29966, "name": "Casanova + Hernandez"}], "category": 17, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 94, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160708153122IUhKL3XHS5Ymiuvr.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>越来越多的小型博物馆出现，为了纪念一个人或展示特定主题的物品。在克罗地亚洛希尼岛，就有一个专门放置一尊青铜像的<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/27073.html\">博物馆</a>，它利用铜像被发现地方的老房子，可以加强当地的文化认同，也让附近民众有更多的参与。</p>\n<p>阿尔巴尼亚第二大城市斯库台（Shkodër）想要纪念一个来自意大利的摄影家族 Marubi 。第一代摄影师 Pietro Marubbi (1834-1903) 在 1850 年左右来到斯库台，建立相片有关的企业 Foto Marubi，直到第三代 Gegë Marubi (1907-1984)都一直用相机记录这个国家的历史和变迁，留下了超过 15 万张照片。政府邀请鹿特丹的建筑事务所 Casanova + Hernandez ，决心用一幢老房子建立一个关于这个家族的摄影博物馆 <a href=\"http://www.marubi.gov.al/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Marubi National Photomuseum</a>。</p>\n<p>从外面看，博物馆是一幢很有历史气息的老房子，在房子的后面连接了一幢新的建筑，与原有房子之间形成了一个花园式的中庭。而这个中庭四周的墙面就显得非常现代，全部变成了一种大小相间排列方形网格，将光线过滤进来，显得轻盈干净。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160708153418bRKlHeAIv7M0QLC3.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.410165\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160708153254fahrueMdy2cUsLIG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714286\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160708153321Qafmkt7PD0SOAnrC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714286\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">这些格子是用铝框隔出来的，有一些玻璃窗的背后是石膏墙，所以造成了透明与不透明相间的场景。</p>\n<p class=\"\">设计者称，他们从镜头光圈的开合获得灵感，它的作用也是控制光线。在这里，一日的光线会随着时间的变化产生明暗强弱的改变，仿佛窗户本身就在控制着光线一样。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160708153937YXpgzNiu1Pq8k4SW.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.964744\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160708153308m4hWBGENKZf1vLsi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714286\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160708153309BIigtAGvZ1FjQqaD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714286\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607081533207HuBTNFnKlyJCxS4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160708153320iygxatBjsW5FMfQL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160708153321nwIUzeBSfoH9v1LT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">从办公室的角度向外看，这种窗户很像中国园林中的花窗。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160708154215d5UYAVGJiK70Mqrl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714286\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p>方格元素延续到了室内，比如墙面嵌入式书架和隔断的墙面。实际上，这种方格本身可以看做是大大小小的照片，它也可以在墙面上间隔排列，让照片墙显得不那么单调。<br></p>\n<p class=\"\">展示区除了黑白色的老照片外还有生前所用的设备、记录视频、书籍等，在这里安静地待上一个下午，感觉时间都停止了。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160708153559Xv2wIu94ndybq8QT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714286\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160708153559B7J12OjexboygSla.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714286\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160708155354Tc1UgDOx9ZtpRLX5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714286\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607081535595zUTEQnoHu1v38qi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714286\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160708153559YE6IOsQrjdLXB03J.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714286\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160708153600gCwOpKX6i9zEoBfR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714286\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160708155407Q9CMjO2k3GXu1dsg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714286\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607081536004cFvXgCAn9eDk3dS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714286\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160708154850liXbSjFNgZOHEKdA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714286\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160708154850StC3DdlgUmWkXnYI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714286\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160708154850DOv4srwMKLXdZ03H.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714286\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607081549041UMR9odxkGtHKQCv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714286\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">图片来自 <a href=\"http://www.dezeen.com/2016/07/06/marubi-national-photomuseum-casanova-hernandez-architects-shkoder-albania-gridded-glass-extension/\" rel=\"nofollow\">dezeen</a></p>\n\n"}